OL,6,FThere will also be "grandfathering" of
OL,7,Fthe disability top up universal credit
OL,8,Ffor existing claimants. So again no
OL,9,Fdetriment to existing claimants.
OL,11,FMy estimate is this would shave
OL,12,Fanother billion pounds or so from the
OL,13,Freform savings by 2029.
OL,15,FFinally, and importantly, the rebels -
OL,16,Fled by Treasury committee chair Meg
OL,17,FHillier - have secured agreement that
OL,18,Fthe Stephen Timms review of how to
OL,19,Fassess entitlement to disability
OL,20,Fbenefits will be a co-production with
OL,21,Fdisability rights groups.
